data.description: Wonderful & Lovely, 2-story home, 3 bedrooms/2.5 baths, conveniently located in the heart of Chula Vista's Rancho Del Rey neighborhood. Close proximity to schools, shopping centers, stores, restaurants, business offices, banks, recreations, freeway, and many more - a prime location !!!   Home was  just  remodeled 2-years ago...upgrades include newer appliances (dishwasher, range oven, built-in microwave);  newer  hardwood flooring throughout the first floor, the staircases, all bedrooms upstairs  & the hallways including baseboards & some electrical accessories.  Newer  bathroom vanities on all 3- baths. Home has vaulted ceilings, central heat & air, & with a great Canyon view from the Master's bedroom.   SOLAR POWER/SOLAR PANELS (leased) was installed one year ago and is transferrable to the new home owners at no cost as long as they qualify.  Sellers wonderfully maintained the property and will gladly turn over this beautiful home once they find a REPLACEMENT HOME SOON !!!   NO HOA, NO MELLO ROOS !!! This is what you are looking for...  Please don't let your Buyers miss out on the opportunity of owning this lovely home !!! Let's go to escrow...
